CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Zhibao Technology Inc. ('Zhibao' or the 'Company') is a leading and high growth InsurTech company primarily engaging in providing digital insurance brokerage services through its operating entities in China. 2B2C digital embedded insurance is the Company's innovative business model, which Zhibao China Group pioneered in China. Zhibao China Group launched the first digital insurance brokerage platform in China in 2020, which is powered by their proprietary PaaS .
